Privacy & Data Disclosure
-------------------------
This application records audio from your microphone and sends it to
Yandex Cloud SpeechKit API (stt.api.cloud.yandex.net) for speech
recognition. Audio data is transmitted over HTTPS to Yandex servers.

By using this application, you acknowledge that:
- Your voice recordings are sent to Yandex Cloud for processing
- Data handling is subject to Yandex Cloud Terms of Service
  (https://yandex.cloud/en/docs/overview/legal)
- You are responsible for providing your own Yandex Cloud API key
  and complying with Yandex Cloud usage terms
- The application stores your API key locally on your device,
  encrypted with Windows DPAPI (CurrentUser scope)
- Recognition history (last 30 entries) is stored locally in
  %APPDATA%/Dictator/


